<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>关凯迪</title><description>关凯迪的个人站：记录 AI 内容系统、个人 IP 写作、内容流程搭建和语音输入工具探索。</description><link>https://guankaidi.com/</link><item><title>AWS 开始系统讲 AgentOps，企业做智能体已经不是“能不能做”，而是“能不能稳定跑”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-06-02-aws-agentops-bedrock-agentcore/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-06-02-aws-agentops-bedrock-agentcore/</guid><description>AWS 在 2026 年 6 月 1 日发布 AgentOps 文章，重点直指成本、调试、治理和持续优化，说明企业智能体正在走向正式运维阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AWS</category><category>AgentOps</category><category>AI运维</category></item><item><title>OpenAI 把 6 月 2 日直播直接对准企业工作流，说明 AI 服务商开始争夺“怎么落地”而不只是“谁更强”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-06-02-openai-intelligence-at-work/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-06-02-openai-intelligence-at-work/</guid><description>OpenAI 在 2026 年 6 月 2 日举办 Intelligence at Work 直播，主题直接落在团队、流程和系统集成，这对做企业 AI 服务的人是很清晰的市场信号。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>OpenAI</category><category>企业AI</category><category>工作流</category></item><item><title>企业智能体卡住的真问题已经不是模型，而是可靠性、权限和治理</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-agent-reliability-and-permissions/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-agent-reliability-and-permissions/</guid><description>5月28日至29日多篇行业报道集中指出，企业智能体进入生产环境后的主要瓶颈是恢复能力、权限体系与治理框架，而不是模型再提升一点点。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI治理</category><category>AI智能体</category><category>风险控制</category></item><item><title>智能体最容易被低估的不是模型费，而是持续运行成本</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-agentic-ai-costs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-agentic-ai-costs/</guid><description>5月29日的一篇行业分析提醒企业，智能体 AI 真正贵的地方在于持续在线、状态管理与基础设施重构。预算如果只算模型费，很容易后期失控。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI智能体</category><category>成本控制</category><category>企业运营</category></item><item><title>大企业先提需求，中小企业再接单：工信部新行动给 AI 服务商一个更现实的入口</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-ai-matchmaking-sme/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-ai-matchmaking-sme/</guid><description>5月28日发布的“百场万企”行动把大企业需求和中小企业供给重新接到一起，AI 服务商更适合从明确场景切入，而不是继续泛谈转型。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI落地</category><category>中小企业</category><category>企业服务</category></item><item><title>Endava把资深员工经验“编码”进智能体，给中小团队一个很强的启发</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-endava-agentic-organization/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-endava-agentic-organization/</guid><description>OpenAI 5月28日发布 Endava 案例，显示企业正在把资深专家判断力沉淀进智能体。对服务型公司和小团队来说，这种做法比单纯追求写代码更有商业价值。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI智能体</category><category>组织升级</category><category>知识沉淀</category></item><item><title>Google把 Preferred Sources 带进 AI 搜索，GEO 从“做内容”进一步变成“争取被选中”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-google-ai-search-preferred-sources/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-google-ai-search-preferred-sources/</guid><description>Google 5月27日更新 AI Search，Preferred Sources 和 Highly Cited 标签进入 AI Mode。企业做 GEO 的重点正在从堆内容转向提升可信度与被偏好的机会。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>GEO</category><category>AI搜索</category><category>内容营销</category></item><item><title>杭州具身智能应用基地展示30多个职业场景，给“AI+实体业务”一个更清晰模板</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-hangzhou-embodied-ai-base/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-hangzhou-embodied-ai-base/</guid><description>5月29日，新华社展示杭州国家级具身智能应用试点基地，130多台机器人覆盖30多个职业场景。对实体企业来说，AI落地正在从软件助手延伸到现场作业协同。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>具身智能</category><category>实体产业</category><category>AI落地</category></item><item><title>从“会回答”到“会干活”：中国石油昆仑大模型给企业 AI 落地提了一个更高标准</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-kunlun-model-active-agents/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-kunlun-model-active-agents/</guid><description>中国石油5月28日发布昆仑大模型升级成果，152个场景规模化落地。对普通企业来说，AI 项目的验收标准也应从回答质量转向主动执行能力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI智能体</category><category>数字化转型</category><category>企业服务</category></item><item><title>NVIDIA内部AI团队的新做法值得学：先在公司里跑通，再把经验变成对外能力</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-nvidia-internal-ai-enablement/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-nvidia-internal-ai-enablement/</guid><description>NVIDIA 5月28日披露其内部企业 AI 自动化团队的运作方式，核心不是包办所有需求，而是内部验证加跨团队赋能，这很适合中小企业做第一阶段 AI 落地。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>NVIDIA</category><category>AI自动化</category><category>企业服务</category></item><item><title>OpenAI最新企业指南说清了一件事：不是所有流程都该上智能体</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-openai-agent-workflow-playbook/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-openai-agent-workflow-playbook/</guid><description>OpenAI 近日发布企业智能体指南，明确区分工作流自动化、LLM步骤和智能体。对中小企业来说，先分清场景，再谈智能化，能少走很多弯路。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>OpenAI</category><category>工作流自动化</category><category>AI落地</category></item><item><title>OpenAI把企业工作区智能体推向通用可用，说明“团队级 AI”正在替代个人试用</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-openai-workspace-agents-ga/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-30-openai-workspace-agents-ga/</guid><description>OpenAI 5月28日更新企业版发布说明，工作区智能体进入更成熟阶段。对企业老板来说，这意味着 AI 工具的购买逻辑开始从个人提效转向团队流程协作。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>OpenAI</category><category>AI智能体</category><category>企业协作</category></item><item><title>企业 AI 开始面对成本压力，老板更关心“值不值”而不是“炫不炫”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-ai-cost-roi-enterprise/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-ai-cost-roi-enterprise/</guid><description>企业 AI 预算正在从盲目试用转向 ROI 审核，AI 服务商需要用场景、指标和成本边界证明落地价值。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>企业AI</category><category>AI成本</category><category>AI落地</category></item><item><title>Google AI 搜索继续改版，GEO 的重点从排名转向“进入答案”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-ai-search-core-update-geo/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-ai-search-core-update-geo/</guid><description>随着 AI Overviews、AI Mode 和核心算法更新同步推进，企业内容策略需要同时兼顾传统搜索排名和 AI 答案引用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>GEO</category><category>AI搜索</category><category>内容策略</category></item><item><title>Automation Anywhere 强化流程自动化，企业智能体需要“可评估、可监控、可回滚”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-automation-anywhere-agentic-process/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-automation-anywhere-agentic-process/</guid><description>Agentic Process Automation 的新能力说明，企业 AI 智能体落地不能只看能不能跑，还要看是否可评估和可治理。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>流程自动化</category><category>AI智能体</category><category>AI治理</category></item><item><title>企业 AI 不能只停在“聊天阶段”，下一步是把洞察变成业务动作</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-beyond-chat-phase-ai/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-beyond-chat-phase-ai/</guid><description>多数企业已经开始使用 AI，但真正规模化并产生财务影响的比例仍然有限，落地关键在于从个人工具走向团队流程。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>企业AI</category><category>AI转型</category><category>业务流程</category></item><item><title>Druid AI 报告提醒：企业 AI 采用率和真实生产效果之间还有距离</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-druid-ai-adoption-benchmark/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-druid-ai-adoption-benchmark/</guid><description>企业 AI 智能体进入生产环境后，真正考验的是使用频率、任务完成率、异常处理和业务反馈，而不是演示效果。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>企业AI</category><category>AI采用率</category><category>生产环境</category></item><item><title>生成式 AI 试点如何走向规模化：先验证小场景，再复制方法</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-genai-pilot-to-scale/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-genai-pilot-to-scale/</guid><description>企业生成式 AI 正从实验阶段走向规模化，关键不是一次做大系统，而是用可验证的小场景建立信任。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>生成式AI</category><category>AI落地</category><category>企业服务</category></item><item><title>Google 新指南称 GEO 仍是 SEO，企业内容要回到“可被理解和信任”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-google-geo-still-seo/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-google-geo-still-seo/</guid><description>Google 对 AI 搜索优化的表态提醒企业，GEO 不应迷信技巧，而应回到高质量内容、可索引结构和真实权威。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>GEO</category><category>SEO</category><category>AI搜索</category></item><item><title>Mphasis 发布企业 AI 平台 Tria，服务商收费模式正在向“结果导向”靠拢</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-mphasis-tria-outcome-ai/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-mphasis-tria-outcome-ai/</guid><description>Mphasis Tria 强调从实验走向业务执行，也提醒 AI 服务商未来要更重视托管结果、收益分成和可量化交付。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>企业AI</category><category>AI服务</category><category>结果导向</category></item><item><title>Salesforce 继续押注 Agentic Enterprise，CRM 正在被 AI 智能体重写</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-salesforce-agentic-enterprise/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-salesforce-agentic-enterprise/</guid><description>Salesforce 对 AI 智能体的投入说明，企业软件的下一轮价值不只是记录数据，而是让系统主动协助业务动作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>Salesforce</category><category>AI智能体</category><category>CRM</category></item><item><title>Workday 与 Google Cloud 扩大合作，企业 AI 落地正在进入“员工日常工作流”</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-workday-google-ai-agents/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-29-workday-google-ai-agents/</guid><description>Workday 把自助服务智能体接入 Gemini Enterprise，说明企业 AI 的竞争重点正在从单点工具转向嵌入 HR、财务等高频流程。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>企业AI</category><category>AI智能体</category><category>工作流</category></item><item><title>我为什么开始做个人 IP 内容</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-why-personal-ip/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-why-personal-ip/</guid><description>不是为了把自己包装得很厉害，而是因为有能力还不够，客户需要持续看见你。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>个人 IP</category><category>内容系统</category><category>交付</category></item><item><title>企业老板都在愁“AI怎么落地”，而市面上很少有人认真做这件事</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-ai-landing-translator/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-ai-landing-translator/</guid><description>中小企业并不缺 AI 焦虑，也不缺尝试意愿，真正缺的是有人能把老板的模糊需求翻译成 AI 可以执行的业务方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI落地</category><category>企业服务</category><category>AI咨询</category></item><item><title>内容系统不是资料夹</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-content-system-not-folder/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-content-system-not-folder/</guid><description>真正能帮你持续输出的，不是存了多少资料，而是资料能不能被转成选题、观点和文章。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>内容系统</category><category>AI 写作</category><category>素材整理</category></item><item><title>为什么我建议先做静态博客</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-static-blog-first/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-static-blog-first/</guid><description>如果目标是长期写内容，而不是折腾服务器，静态博客通常是更轻、更安全的起点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>建站</category><category>Cloudflare Pages</category><category>内容系统</category></item><item><title>想让 AI 写得像你，先让它看懂你的改稿</title><link>https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-teach-ai-your-style/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://guankaidi.com/blog/2026-05-25-teach-ai-your-style/</guid><description>与其反复说“自然一点”，不如把原稿和改稿放在一起，让 AI 学你真正做过的选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>AI 写作</category><category>写作偏好</category><category>工作流</category></item></channel></rss>